headline: 12 Amazingly Self-Aware Clickbait Headlines That Always Work! Tabs, Thurs., Jan. 20, 2022
author: Doktor Zoom
sentences:
[Texas Tribune]

It was in the year 1619 that the first Black slave was brought to the shores of this nation.

[...]
White Americans must recognize that justice for black people cannot be achieved without radical changes in the structure of our society...The evils of capitalism are as real as the evils of militarism and racism
The problems of racial injustice and economic injustice cannot be solved without a radical redistribution of political and economic power.
